Atoms:

- Button
- Input
- Icon
- Badge (example: “Officially Licensed”)
- Text (Title, Body, Price)
- Image
- Spinner / LoadingIndicator
- Divider
- Tag / Chip (Category, Size, etc.)

Molecules:

- SearchBar (Input + Button/Icon)
- FilterDropdown (Label + Select)
- FilterChipsRow (Tag/Chip list + clear button)
- PriceDisplay (Price text + optional discount badge)
- RatingPreview (stars + count -- used as placeholder)
- ProductThumbnail (Image + Badge overlay)

Organisms:

- CatalogHeader
  - SearchBar
  - FilterDropdown(s)
  - FilterChipsRow

- ProductCard
  - ProductThumbnail
  - Text (name)
  - PriceDisplay
  - Badge (Officially Licensed)
  - Button (“View Details” / “Add to Cart” if you include it here)

- PaginationControls (or InfiniteScrollLoader if you prefer)
- CategorySidebar (optional if you want categories on the left)
- EmptyState (no results found)
- ErrorState (API error message)
- LoadingState (spinner + skeletons)

Templates:

- CatalogPageTemplate
  - CatalogHeader (search + filters)
  - CategorySidebar (optional)
  - ProductGrid
  - PaginationControls
  - Loading/Error/Empty states

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Atomic Design Hierarchy view of "Product Catalog":

TEMPLATE
└─ CatalogPageTemplate
   ├─ CatalogHeader (Organism)
   ├─ CategorySidebar (Organism - optional)
   ├─ ProductGrid (Organism)
   ├─ PaginationControls (Organism)
   ├─ LoadingState (Organism)
   ├─ EmptyState (Organism)
   └─ ErrorState (Organism)

ORGANISMS
├─ CatalogHeader
│  ├─ SearchBar (Molecule)
│  ├─ FilterDropdown(s) (Molecule)
│  └─ FilterChipsRow (Molecule)
│
├─ ProductGrid
│  └─ ProductCard (Molecule)
│
├─ ProductCard
│  ├─ ProductThumbnail (Molecule)
│  ├─ Text (Atom)
│  ├─ PriceDisplay (Molecule)
│  ├─ Badge (Atom)
│  └─ Button (Atom)
│
├─ PaginationControls
│  └─ Button (Atom)
│
├─ CategorySidebar
│  ├─ Text (Atom)
│  └─ Tag/Chip (Atom)
│
├─ LoadingState
│  └─ Spinner / LoadingIndicator (Atom)
│
├─ EmptyState
│  ├─ Text (Atom)
│  └─ Icon (Atom)
│
└─ ErrorState
   ├─ Text (Atom)
   ├─ Icon (Atom)
   └─ Button (Atom)

MOLECULES
├─ SearchBar
│  ├─ Input (Atom)
│  ├─ Button (Atom)
│  └─ Icon (Atom)
│
├─ FilterDropdown
│  ├─ Text (Atom)
│  └─ Input (Atom)
│
├─ FilterChipsRow
│  ├─ Tag/Chip (Atom)
│  └─ Button (Atom)
│
├─ PriceDisplay
│  ├─ Text (Atom)
│  └─ Badge (Atom)
│
├─ RatingPreview
│  ├─ Icon (Atom)
│  └─ Text (Atom)
│
└─ ProductThumbnail
   ├─ Image (Atom)
   └─ Badge (Atom)

